an intentional evening🍓✨

the phone’s on silent, the mind is in the present, sky is painted in soft pastels, tea poured slowly, pastries that melt in your mouth…

reminder to choose slow moments, warm light, gentle reflections and quiet gratitude- this is where alignment lives <3
